# 🚀 Project Sentinel

## Enterprise-Grade Incremental Data Ingestion Pipeline using Databricks Auto Loader & Delta Lake

![Databricks](https://img.shields.io/badge/Databricks-FF3621?style=for-the-badge&logo=databricks&logoColor=white)
