# 📖 Overview

Project Sentinel is an enterprise-grade incremental data ingestion pipeline built using **Databricks Auto Loader**, **PySpark**, and **Delta Lake** following the **Bronze–Silver–Gold Medallion Architecture**.

The pipeline automatically detects newly arrived transaction files, ingests only new data using checkpointing, cleans and validates the records, and generates business-ready analytical datasets.

The project demonstrates modern Data Engineering concepts including:

- Incremental Data Ingestion
- Databricks Auto Loader
- Delta Lake
- Schema Enforcement
- Schema Evolution
- Late Data Handling
- Structured Streaming
- Data Cleaning
- Deduplication
- Pipeline Monitoring
- Pipeline Logging
- Failure Handling
- SQL Analytics

---

# 🏗 Architecture

![Architecture](architecture/architecture.png)

---

# 🥉 Bronze Layer

Raw data ingestion using Databricks Auto Loader.

Features:

- Auto Loader (cloudFiles)
- Schema Enforcement
- Incremental Processing
- Checkpointing
- Ingestion Timestamp
- Delta Table Storage

---

# 🥈 Silver Layer

Data Cleansing & Validation

Features:

- Remove Duplicate Records
- Handle Null Values
- Type Casting
- Standardization
- Data Quality Checks

---

# 🥇 Gold Layer

Business-ready analytics.

Generated KPIs:

- Top Products
- Top Customers
- Payment Distribution
- Revenue Analysis

---

